<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>2024 on Kaya Log</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/tags/2024/</link><description>Recent content in 2024 on Kaya Log</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://yshghid.github.io/tags/2024/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>github blog 커스텀하기: archive 창 수정</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/study/hugo/hugo-custom3/</link><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/study/hugo/hugo-custom3/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="github-blog-커스텀하기-archive-창-수정">
 github blog 커스텀하기: archive 창 수정
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#github-blog-%ec%bb%a4%ec%8a%a4%ed%85%80%ed%95%98%ea%b8%b0-archive-%ec%b0%bd-%ec%88%98%ec%a0%95">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/06aaccaa-8c31-43e4-9815-6924dc00589b" alt="image" />&lt;/p>
&lt;p>hugo-book 테마에서 tag, category에 따른 archive창을 볼수있는데 위와같이 구성돼있다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>내용없이 제목만 뜨게 만들고싶어서 &lt;a href="https://github.com/alex-shpak/hugo-book/tree/master/layouts">hugo-book 테마의 layout 디렉토리&lt;/a>를 찾아보니 &lt;a href="https://github.com/alex-shpak/hugo-book/blob/master/layouts/taxonomy/taxonomy.html">taxonomy/taxonomy.html&lt;/a>과 &lt;a href="https://github.com/alex-shpak/hugo-book/blob/master/layouts/posts/list.html">post/list.html&lt;/a>이 관여하고있는듯해서, 내 리포지토리에 taxonomy/taxonomy.html과 layouts/post/list.html을 생성해서 각각 다음과 같이 작성해주었다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-html" data-lang="html">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>{{ define &amp;#34;main&amp;#34; }}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> {{ range sort .Paginator.Pages }}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &amp;lt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672">article&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">class&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;markdown book-post&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&amp;gt;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &amp;lt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672">h2&lt;/span>&amp;gt;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &amp;lt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672">a&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">href&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;{{ .RelPermalink }}&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&amp;gt;{{ partial &amp;#34;docs/title.html&amp;#34; . }}&amp;lt;/&lt;span style="color:#f92672">a&lt;/span>&amp;gt;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &amp;lt;/&lt;span style="color:#f92672">h2&lt;/span>&amp;gt;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> {{ partial &amp;#34;docs/post-meta&amp;#34; . }}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &amp;lt;/&lt;span style="color:#f92672">article&lt;/span>&amp;gt;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> {{ end }}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> {{ template &amp;#34;_internal/pagination.html&amp;#34; . }}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>{{ end }}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>{{ define &amp;#34;toc&amp;#34; }}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> {{ partial &amp;#34;docs/taxonomy&amp;#34; . }}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>{{ end }}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>참고로 위코드는 원래코드에서 아래 내용을 뺀것이다.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>github blog 커스텀하기: font size, link-color 수정</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/study/hugo/hugo-custom2/</link><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/study/hugo/hugo-custom2/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="github-blog-커스텀하기-font-size-link-color-수정">
 github blog 커스텀하기: font size, link-color 수정
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#github-blog-%ec%bb%a4%ec%8a%a4%ed%85%80%ed%95%98%ea%b8%b0-font-size-link-color-%ec%88%98%ec%a0%95">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>hugo-book 테마는 깔끔한 흰색배경이 포인트라서 css를 딱히 커스텀해줄건 없긴하지만&amp;hellip;&lt;/p>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>코드창의 폰트사이즈가 조금 작으면 더 이쁠것같아서 수정해주려하고&lt;/li>
&lt;li>하이퍼링크는 파란색, 방문한링크는 보라색으로 뜨는데 보라색이 뭔가 맘에안들어서 진한 남색 정도로 바꿔줄것이다.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;h2 id="1-코드-폰트크기-수정">
 1. 코드 폰트크기 수정
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#1-%ec%bd%94%eb%93%9c-%ed%8f%b0%ed%8a%b8%ed%81%ac%ea%b8%b0-%ec%88%98%ec%a0%95">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://github.com/alex-shpak/hugo-book/tree/master?tab=readme-ov-file#extra-customisation">hugo-book 테마의 extra customization을 보면&lt;/a> assets/_custom.scss 경로에 커스텀하려는 부분만 적어주면 되는듯하다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://github.com/alex-shpak/hugo-book/tree/master/assets">hugo-book/assets를 보면&lt;/a> scss 파일이 많다. 그중 _markdown.scss를 보면 코드관련 설정이 있다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-scss" data-lang="scss">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">code&lt;/span> {
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">direction&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">:&lt;/span> ltr;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">unicode-bidi&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">:&lt;/span> embed;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">padding&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">:&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">0&lt;/span> $padding-4;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">background&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">:&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">var&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#f92672">--&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">gray&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">-&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">200&lt;/span>);
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">border-radius&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">:&lt;/span> $border-radius;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">font-size&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">:&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">0&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">.875&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">em&lt;/span>;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> }
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>여기서 font-size를 0.775em으로 수정해줄것이다. 블로그 리포지토리에 assets/_custom.scss를 생성해서 해당 내용을 추가해줬다.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>github blog 커스텀하기: favicon, giscus 댓글창 추가</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/study/hugo/hugo-custom/</link><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/study/hugo/hugo-custom/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="github-blog-커스텀하기-favicon-giscus-댓글창-추가">
 github blog 커스텀하기: favicon, giscus 댓글창 추가
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#github-blog-%ec%bb%a4%ec%8a%a4%ed%85%80%ed%95%98%ea%b8%b0-favicon-giscus-%eb%8c%93%ea%b8%80%ec%b0%bd-%ec%b6%94%ea%b0%80">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="1-favicon-설정">
 1. favicon 설정
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#1-favicon-%ec%84%a4%ec%a0%95">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Hugo-book 테마의 github에서 README 파일을 읽어보면, &lt;a href="https://github.com/alex-shpak/hugo-book#site-configuration">logo&lt;/a>와 &lt;a href="https://github.com/alex-shpak/hugo-book#extra-customisation">favicon 이미지&lt;/a>의 경로 정보를 찾을 수 있다.
확인 결과 &lt;code>static&lt;/code> 디렉토리에 각각 &lt;code>logo.png&lt;/code>, &lt;code>favicon.png&lt;/code>로 저장해두면 반영되는것 같다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>참고로 Hugo-book 테마의 오리지널 웹사이트는 아래와 같이 디자인되어있고&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/1028de04-3335-4db4-bbf7-bb101c54e8a2" alt="image" />&lt;/p>
&lt;p>최상단 탭에 들어가는 이미지가 logo.png, 블로그 이름 옆에 들어가는 이미지(위 이미지에는 없음)가 favicon.png이다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>먼저 static 디렉토리에 넣고 싶은 로고와 파비콘을 logo.png, favicon.png 로 저장해준다. 다음으로, hugo.toml 파일을 열어 아래 내용을 추가해준다.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>101개의 쿠키그릇 문제</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/study/think-bayes/bayes-cookie_problem/</link><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/study/think-bayes/bayes-cookie_problem/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="들어가며">
 들어가며
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#%eb%93%a4%ec%96%b4%ea%b0%80%eb%a9%b0">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>101개의 쿠키그릇 문제는 아래와 같다. 이를 pmf 객체를 사용해서 답을 내보자! pmf 객체는 사건과 그 사건이 발생할 확률을 나타내는 데이터 구조이다.&lt;/p>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>쿠키 문제&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>101개의 그릇에는 바닐라, 초콜릿 두 종류의 쿠키가 존재한다. 그릇 0에는 바닐라 쿠키가 0% 들어 있다. 그릇 1에는 바닐라 쿠키가 1% 들어 있다.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>이런 식으로 진행하여 그릇 99에는 바닐라 쿠키가 99개 들어 있고, 그릇 100에는 바닐라 쿠키가 100개 들어 있다.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>무작위로 한 그릇을 선택하고 무작위로 쿠키를 하나 선택했을 때 바닐라 쿠키였다. 그 쿠키가 그릇 n에서 나왔을 확률은 얼마인가?&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;h2 id="1-pmf-클래스의-기본-사용법">
 1. Pmf 클래스의 기본 사용법
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#1-pmf-%ed%81%b4%eb%9e%98%ec%8a%a4%ec%9d%98-%ea%b8%b0%eb%b3%b8-%ec%82%ac%ec%9a%a9%eb%b2%95">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="11-pmf-객체-생성하기">
 1.1 Pmf 객체 생성하기
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#11-pmf-%ea%b0%9d%ec%b2%b4-%ec%83%9d%ec%84%b1%ed%95%98%ea%b8%b0">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h3>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">from&lt;/span> empiricaldist &lt;span style="color:#f92672">import&lt;/span> Pmf
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>coin &lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span> Pmf()
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>coin[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;heads&amp;#39;&lt;/span>] &lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">1&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">/&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">2&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>coin[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;tails&amp;#39;&lt;/span>] &lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">1&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">/&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">2&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>pmf 객체는 각 사건과 그 사건이 발생할 확률을 나타내는 데이터 구조이다. &amp;ldquo;동전 던지기&amp;quot;라는 문제에서 &amp;ldquo;앞면&amp;quot;이라는 사건이 발생할 확률에 대한 데이터 구조를 coin이라는 이름으로 생성해줘보겠다.
coin이라는 Pmf 객체를 생성한 후, &amp;lsquo;heads&amp;rsquo;와 &amp;rsquo;tails&amp;rsquo;에 각각 0.5의 확률을 할당해주었다.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Execution time of max() function</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/study/learning-algorithm/algorithm-ch01/</link><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/study/learning-algorithm/algorithm-ch01/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="execution-time-of-max-function">
 Execution time of max() function
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#execution-time-of-max-function">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="1-두종류의-인스턴스에-max-실행">
 1. 두종류의 인스턴스에 max() 실행
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#1-%eb%91%90%ec%a2%85%eb%a5%98%ec%9d%98-%ec%9d%b8%ec%8a%a4%ed%84%b4%ec%8a%a4%ec%97%90-max-%ec%8b%a4%ed%96%89">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">def&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">run_init_trial&lt;/span>(output&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">True&lt;/span>):
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;First Table in chapter 1.&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> n &lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">100&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> tbl &lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span> DataTable([&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">12&lt;/span>, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">12&lt;/span>, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">12&lt;/span>], [&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;N&amp;#39;&lt;/span>, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;Ascending&amp;#39;&lt;/span>, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;Descending&amp;#39;&lt;/span>], output&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>output, decimals&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">3&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">while&lt;/span> n &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;lt;=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">1000000&lt;/span>:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> m_up &lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span> measure_time(n, order&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;ascending&amp;#39;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> m_down &lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span> measure_time(n, order&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;descending&amp;#39;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> tbl&lt;span style="color:#f92672">.&lt;/span>row([n, m_up, m_down])
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> n &lt;span style="color:#f92672">*=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">10&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">return&lt;/span> tbl
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>오름차순 정수, 내림차순 정수 리스트가 있다. 두 문제 인스턴스에 max()를 수행한 시간 결과를 위 코드로 확인할수있다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>while문을 통해 오름차순 리스트와 내림차순 리스트에서 native_largest 함수의 실행 시간을 측정하여 m_up, m_down으로 받고 tbl에 저장한다. 리스트의 길이 n을 10배씩 증가시켜가며 n= 1000000까지 수행한다.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Hugo로 github blog 개설하기</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/study/hugo/hugo-blog/</link><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/study/hugo/hugo-blog/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="hugo로-github-blog-개설하기">
 Hugo로 github blog 개설하기
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#hugo%eb%a1%9c-github-blog-%ea%b0%9c%ec%84%a4%ed%95%98%ea%b8%b0">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="1-사전-설치">
 1. 사전 설치
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#1-%ec%82%ac%ec%a0%84-%ec%84%a4%ec%b9%98">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>$ brew install hugo
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>$ hugo version
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>hugo v0.131.0+extended darwin/arm64 BuildDate&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>2024-08-02T09:03:48Z VendorInfo&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>brew
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>Hugo v0.112.0 이상인지 확인하면 된다.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="2-사이트-생성">
 2. 사이트 생성
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#2-%ec%82%ac%ec%9d%b4%ed%8a%b8-%ec%83%9d%ec%84%b1">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>작업하고 싶은 위치에 Hugo 디렉토리를 만들어준다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>$ pwd
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>/Users/yshmbid
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>$ mkdir Hugo
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>$ cd Hugo
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>Hugo로 들어가서 hugo 사이트 틀을 생성해준다. 나는 blog라는 이름으로 생성하였다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>$ pwd
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>/Users/yshmbid/Hugo
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>$ hugo new site blog
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>blog 디렉토리에 빈 Git 저장소를 초기화한다.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>jupyter notebook 설치 후 python, R 가상환경 연결하기</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/study/python-r/anaconda-jupyter/</link><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/study/python-r/anaconda-jupyter/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="jupyter-notebook-설치-후-python-r-가상환경-연결하기">
